comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_PEER_GROUP_STATE.ibank_offer
  is '拆放同业-其中：同业拆借';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_PEER_GROUP_STATE.ibankbrw_money
