comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_PEER_GROUP_STATE.buyresalezy
  is '一般风险暴露-其中：买入返售(质押式)';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_PEER_GROUP_STATE.ibankbond
