comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_PEER_GROUP_STATE.policyfidebt
  is '同业债券-其中：政策性金融债';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_PEER_GROUP_STATE.ibankreceipt
  is '一般风险暴露-其中：同业存单';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_LESS_LES_PEER_GROUP_STATE.sumprod
